Intentionally invalid ABIN input
(requires PIMD without thermostat)

Here we test that ABIN sends TC error tag early
So that the TC server exits gracefully.

&general
!pot='mmwater'
pot='_tera_'
watpot=1
ipimd=1,
nstep=1,
dt=40.,
irandom=13131313,

nwrite=1,
nwritef=1,
nwritev=1,
nwritex=1,
nrest=1,
idebug=3
/

&nhcopt
inose=0,
temp=0.0d0
/
